42:34.052 --> 42:37.522
Spence, where are you going?!
Come -

42:37.555 --> 42:40.225
Jory what the heck happened?!

42:50.235 --> 42:56.908
(thunder)

43:17.295 --> 43:18.797
You.

43:19.297 --> 43:22.934
So this is what happens,

43:22.968 --> 43:25.403
