44:08.013 --> 44:09.180
It's worth a million dollars.

44:09.214 --> 44:11.449
You wanted it.
You know you did.

44:11.482 --> 44:13.719
Just get the fuck out of here.

44:15.887 --> 44:18.356
I brought this for you
I want you to have it!

44:18.389 --> 44:20.391
(door opening)

44:20.425 --> 44:24.129
(thunder)

44:24.162 --> 44:30.535
(inner screaming)
(heavy breathing)

44:31.069 --> 44:42.881
(strange organic squelching)

44:44.049 --> 44:45.383
(door slams)

44:45.751 --> 44:47.518
(pukes)

44:48.887 --> 44:58.529
(gasping)

44:59.064 --> 45:01.199
JORY: Spence?

45:04.602 --> 45:06.571
(THUD)

45:15.246 --> 45:18.884
Spence! Keys!

45:18.917 --> 45:20.886
(sputtering)

45:27.959 --> 45:30.561
Hi Spence.
I'm Dr. Sidkin.

45:30.595 --> 45:34.365
This is Dr Zimmermann,
our neuropsychologist.

45:34.399 --> 45:36.367
BETTY:We had them give
you some Lorazepam.

45:36.401 --> 45:38.403
Are you feeling calmer?

45:38.436 --> 45:40.371
I guess yeah.

45:40.405 --> 45:42.573
We just had a few
questions for you.

45:43.408 --> 45:48.113
In the past week have you
done any recreational drugs?

45:48.146 --> 45:50.882
More specifically,
Saturday the tenth?

45:50.916 --> 45:56.087
and uh, particularly ecstasy,
at the Uncle Jay's Club?

45:57.588 --> 45:59.557
You got me.

45:59.590 --> 46:01.392
We've had several
patients come in tonight

46:01.426 --> 46:04.062
and the past few days
who have the same symptoms.

46:04.095 --> 46:08.066
They had taken something
called Genuine Pink Doves.

46:08.099 --> 46:10.601
Does this sound familiar?

46:11.336 --> 46:14.772
I seem to remember
something about that.

46:16.641 --> 46:18.276
Alright,

46:18.309 --> 46:22.247
What you're experiencing is
hyperactive cortical activity.

46:22.280 --> 46:27.085
This explains the
heightened emotional state.

46:27.118 --> 46:29.620
You feeling more
emotional than usual?

46:29.654 --> 46:32.157
Happier? Sadder? Angrier?

46:32.190 --> 46:33.591
Maybe.

46:33.624 --> 46:38.129
What about a feeling
of impending doom?

46:38.163 --> 46:40.431
Let's go with that.

46:40.465 --> 46:42.000
BETTY: Can we keep
you overnight, Spence?

46:42.033 --> 46:44.702
You know, whatever voodoo pill
you gave me seemed to work so,

46:45.971 --> 46:49.274
The Lorazepam only has a calming
effect until it wears off.

46:49.307 --> 46:52.110
I'm telling you, I feel fine.

46:52.143 --> 46:56.214
Just a few tests.
It's for your own safety.

46:59.484 --> 47:00.952
Do what you gotta do.

47:00.986 --> 47:02.820
Thank you.

48:15.060 --> 48:15.893
AZARIA: Spence?

48:15.927 --> 48:17.462
SPENCE: Azaria...

48:18.396 --> 48:20.565
Oh god, thank god
you're here. Come here.

48:24.469 --> 48:27.372
What happened to Chuck? Do
they know what happened to him?

48:27.405 --> 48:28.940
They're checking his heart.

48:28.974 --> 48:30.976
What happened to you?

48:32.077 --> 48:33.211
I don't know what
got into your brother,

48:33.244 --> 48:36.214
he just,
he started attacking me.

48:36.247 --> 48:38.549
Has he said anything?
Where is he? Is he here?

48:38.583 --> 48:40.285
He's not with you?

48:40.318 --> 48:41.552
No, I haven't seen him.

48:41.586 --> 48:43.388
Spence, he took your car.

48:43.421 --> 48:44.389
What if he got in
a car accident...

48:44.422 --> 48:45.490
He took my car?!

48:45.523 --> 48:46.891
He took my car?!
Yeah I saw him get in -no,

48:46.924 --> 48:48.226
No, he didn't take my car.
Yeah I saw him get in -no,

48:48.259 --> 48:49.427
No, he didn't take my car.
Spence I saw him get...

48:49.460 --> 48:50.128
Hey hey alright listen listen
I saw him -No!

48:50.161 --> 48:51.229
We an call the police,

48:51.262 --> 48:52.998
give them the plates,
track it down.

48:53.031 --> 48:55.967
No! No, it would get the police
involved, he's gonna go back.

48:56.001 --> 48:56.901
I can't do that.

48:56.934 --> 48:57.268
I can't do that.
Hey...

48:57.302 --> 48:58.269
Hey...

48:59.770 --> 49:01.939
We've got this.

49:04.275 --> 49:07.645
Have you told anyone?
Have you?

49:07.678 --> 49:09.280
No.

49:10.515 --> 49:12.250
What can I get you?
Some water?

49:12.283 --> 49:13.151
Let me get
you something.

49:13.184 --> 49:14.252
Spence... you're half naked.

49:14.285 --> 49:15.253
Let me get you something.

49:15.286 --> 49:17.322
Let me take
care of you.

49:17.355 --> 49:19.657
Don't go please.
I don't want you to go.

49:19.690 --> 49:24.962
I'll be right back.
I'll be right back, alright?

49:24.996 --> 49:26.998
Right back...

50:14.512 --> 50:16.347
SPENCE: What?

50:17.915 --> 50:26.424
(panicked breathing)

50:44.075 --> 50:45.910
Sit down.

50:46.611 --> 50:48.779
Can you grab me
some Lorazepam please?!

50:49.880 --> 50:51.249
Why won't this stop!?

50:51.282 --> 50:53.218
Take a deep breath.

50:55.920 --> 50:56.921
BETTY: Open your mouth.

50:56.954 --> 50:58.189
ARG!!!

50:58.223 --> 51:00.091
BETTY: Open your mouth an lift
up the tongue.

51:00.125 --> 51:03.194
Let it dissolve.

51:03.228 --> 51:05.029
BETTY: Breath,
listen up and breath.

51:05.062 --> 51:07.232
BETTY: Breath...

51:10.135 --> 51:11.736
BETTY: Breath...

51:14.739 --> 51:17.775
I need more of those.
Give me more of those.

51:20.077 --> 51:24.249
I don't care what it takes. I'll
stand on my head for a month.

51:24.282 --> 51:26.050
I'll rip out my
own fucking jugular.

51:26.083 --> 51:28.919
whatever it takes.
Just make this stop.

51:28.953 --> 51:30.921
Look, I can't
just make this stop.

51:33.958 --> 51:36.394
The other patients
who took this Pink Dove

51:36.427 --> 51:38.563
are participating
in a research study I'm doing,

51:38.596 --> 51:39.830
that I think will help you.

51:39.864 --> 51:42.667
I'm not here to be
your human lab rat, FUCK!

51:43.768 --> 51:45.903
This is me trying to get
you through this Spence.

51:45.936 --> 51:47.472
Then give me
more of that shit.

51:47.505 --> 51:48.606
That shit works!

51:48.639 --> 51:50.275
It's not going
to help you.

51:50.308 --> 51:52.243
Okay, as you can see,
it only lasts so long

51:52.277 --> 51:54.078
until it wears off.
Give it enough time and

51:54.111 --> 51:56.647
it'll start losing
its effects altogether.

51:57.282 --> 52:00.818
If you don't find a
way to make me feel finer

52:00.851 --> 52:03.621
than a frog hair
split four ways...

52:06.457 --> 52:07.825
(CRASH)

52:10.495 --> 52:12.930
You're not holding
any cards here, Spence.

52:12.963 --> 52:14.665
You make up your mind quick,

52:14.699 --> 52:18.135
you comply and be
civil, or you walk.

52:25.676 --> 52:28.446
We need to keep you off
the medication for the tests.

52:28.479 --> 52:31.316
To see your reactions
as they happen naturally.

52:31.349 --> 52:34.652
Without
the paradoxical effects.

53:25.270 --> 53:26.871
Where were you?

53:27.372 --> 53:28.673
I've been here.

53:28.706 --> 53:31.876
Don't lie to me Jory.

53:32.410 --> 53:34.779
Stop fucking lying to me!

53:43.721 --> 53:46.391
Oh I am such an idiot!

53:47.892 --> 53:49.260
Don't touch me.

53:52.430 --> 53:54.399
Yeah, don't touch me.

54:01.238 --> 54:03.207
Every FUCKING man in my life.

54:03.240 --> 54:06.277
Every FUCKING
single FUCKING TIME!

54:06.311 --> 54:09.246
WHAT DID I DO?!?

54:13.618 --> 54:15.486
(electronic beeping)

54:30.267 --> 54:31.502
Don't fucking look at me!

54:31.536 --> 54:32.470
Don't fucking look at me!
Don't give me that.

54:38.609 --> 54:39.844
I knew the g-

54:39.877 --> 54:40.745
I knew there was
something wrong with that guy

54:40.778 --> 54:41.979
the moment I fucking met him.

54:42.012 --> 54:44.915
Jory where did you go
when you took his car?

54:44.949 --> 54:46.083
WHERE DID YOU GO?!

54:46.116 --> 54:48.753
WHERE DID YOU GO?!
I WAS GOING AFTER HIM!

54:48.786 --> 54:50.788
I don't believe you...

55:16.046 --> 55:18.148
Is that strawberry?

55:19.149 --> 55:20.985
Excuse me?

55:23.821 --> 55:25.390
Your shampoo.

55:27.157 --> 55:28.493
Um...

56:17.708 --> 56:21.045
It's important that
you lie still, Spence.

56:26.383 --> 56:28.185
BETTY: Spence,

56:28.218 --> 56:32.122
Does antisocial personality
disorder mean anything to you?

56:33.057 --> 56:35.760
No.

56:35.793 --> 56:37.595
Should it?

56:40.130 --> 56:43.200
I would like to conduct
a psycho-diagnostic tool

56:43.233 --> 56:47.237
we use to,
assess psychopathy.

56:47.638 --> 56:50.040
I ask that you don't take
this assessment too personally.

56:50.074 --> 56:52.242
It might not
reveal anything at all.

56:53.478 --> 56:56.146
What makes you think
I'm a psychopath?

57:01.418 --> 57:04.254
BETTY: Did you ever get into
any conflicts in school?

57:04.755 --> 57:07.625
No.

57:07.658 --> 57:14.331
Nothing beyond typical horsing
around. You know. Kids' stuff.

57:15.633 --> 57:17.735
Can you remember any
particular time you may have

57:17.768 --> 57:20.437
intentionally hurt someone?

57:23.340 --> 57:26.811
There is this one time I
dislocated this kids' shoulder.

57:26.844 --> 57:28.445
We were playing soccer,

57:28.479 --> 57:32.282
and he kept cheating,
going out of bounds.

57:32.316 --> 57:33.918
Until finally, I
caught up to him,

57:33.951 --> 57:36.654
and kicked his little
feet out from under him.

57:36.687 --> 57:39.957
He landed so hard
you could hear it pop.

57:40.190 --> 57:46.330
It was embarrassing. But hey.
He had no right to complain.

57:47.297 --> 57:50.167
I taught him a valuable lesson.

57:50.635 --> 57:54.138
I'm sure he never went
out of bounds again.

57:56.674 --> 57:59.977
Just use the push button device
to rate the images you see.

58:00.010 --> 58:01.512
Rate them
from one to five

58:01.546 --> 58:04.314
based on how
upsetting you find them.

58:04.348 --> 58:07.785
BETTY: Have you ever
tried to help somebody?

58:07.818 --> 58:10.154
Very recently actually.

58:11.488 --> 58:13.524
Tell me about that.

58:13.558 --> 58:15.793
I tried to help this
troubled kid kill somebody-

58:15.826 --> 58:17.895
Stop. You don't
want to tell me this.

58:20.831 --> 58:24.134
BETTY: What is it about him
that made you want to help?

58:24.168 --> 58:26.671
I was going to be
well compensated.

58:26.704 --> 58:29.339
And what if you weren't
going to be well compensated?

58:29.373 --> 58:31.909
Do you really think
I'm that fucking stupid?

58:33.010 --> 58:34.378
No.

58:35.746 --> 58:36.847
BETTY: Could you agree that

58:36.881 --> 58:38.849
you're taking
advantage of people?

58:40.517 --> 58:42.887
Why wouldn't I?

58:42.920 --> 58:44.989
SPENCE: I can see in their walk,

58:45.022 --> 58:48.025
if someone's for
the taking, or not...

58:48.058 --> 58:50.227
Even if they don't know it.

58:50.260 --> 58:55.065
They just kinda...
put it out there.

58:55.099 --> 58:58.168
SPENCE: My babysitter, she
tried to give me shit after

58:58.202 --> 59:01.739
she caught me playing
with matches in the closet,

59:01.772 --> 59:04.374
so I let her in
to retrieve them,

59:05.743 --> 59:08.212
and I locked her in.

59:08.879 --> 59:11.215
And I left
her in all night,

59:11.882 --> 59:15.686
until my father
got home the next day.

59:15.720 --> 59:17.922
She had shit her pants.

59:21.391 --> 59:27.564
It was just pathetic, how
she shit her pants like that.

59:38.809 --> 59:44.081
SPENCE: People say that they
feel this, or that...

59:45.916 --> 59:48.418
But in my life...

59:49.920 --> 59:52.489
I basically feel nothing.

59:52.757 --> 59:56.560
(emergency alarm)

59:56.593 --> 59:59.830
(struggled breathing)

01:00:08.272 --> 01:00:11.275
(thunder)

01:00:11.776 --> 01:00:14.444
(struggled sobbing)

01:00:15.612 --> 01:00:17.281
Spence...

01:00:20.284 --> 01:00:21.952
BETTY: What's happening?

01:00:36.300 --> 01:00:39.970
CHUCK: Forget
going to the police.

01:00:40.004 --> 01:00:43.173
Do you not see
the world we live in?

01:00:43.207 --> 01:00:47.277
We're on our own,
survival of the fittest.

01:00:47.311 --> 01:00:51.782
And I'm intent on surviving.

01:00:51.816 --> 01:00:55.152
Meaning what?

01:00:55.185 --> 01:00:59.489
Meaning there's no need for
this to get out in the open.

01:00:59.523 --> 01:01:01.726
We'll find him ourselves.

01:01:03.193 --> 01:01:05.495
And then what? Get
together and play Nintendo?

01:01:05.529 --> 01:01:06.997
Shut up.

01:01:07.865 --> 01:01:11.368
She gives excellent advice Jory.

01:01:12.002 --> 01:01:15.472
Magnum PI is talking a
little frontier justice.

01:01:15.505 --> 01:01:16.974
Murder on the home front.

01:01:17.007 --> 01:01:17.875
Wouldn't be the first time,

01:01:17.908 --> 01:01:20.711
would it daddy?
Jory shut up!

01:01:24.081 --> 01:01:26.516
You shouldn't even
be here right now.

01:01:29.686 --> 01:01:34.992
CHUCK: Well, I am son.

01:01:35.025 --> 01:01:37.494
CHUCK: I don't blame you.

01:01:37.527 --> 01:01:39.897
I wanted my father dead too.

01:01:39.930 --> 01:01:42.032
You know why?

01:01:42.066 --> 01:01:45.502
CHUCK: Because he
was just like you.

01:01:45.535 --> 01:01:49.339
He was glass.

01:01:49.373 --> 01:01:52.843
Wasn't his fault.

01:01:52.877 --> 01:01:56.380
He just was.

01:01:59.549 --> 01:02:01.618
(crash)

01:02:04.121 --> 01:02:05.890
(smack)

01:02:10.127 --> 01:02:11.896
Spence!

01:02:14.564 --> 01:02:16.200
Hi Jory.

01:02:16.233 --> 01:02:18.869
I need to talk to you.

01:02:18.903 --> 01:02:20.370
I can't,
I have a session,

01:02:20.404 --> 01:02:22.472
I need to talk to you now.

01:02:27.644 --> 01:02:28.412
Give me a minute.

01:02:28.445 --> 01:02:29.413
Give me a minute.
No.

01:02:32.817 --> 01:02:34.251
Jory: You're still here?!

01:02:34.284 --> 01:02:35.385
Jory: You're still here?!
Actually I'm just on my way out.

01:02:35.419 --> 01:02:36.420
I thought you'd already left.

01:02:36.453 --> 01:02:37.721
Azaria said she
saw you take off.

01:02:37.754 --> 01:02:39.589
Yeah well clearly
Azaria was wrong.

01:02:39.623 --> 01:02:41.058
Okay I don't know what
the fuck this is but-

01:02:41.091 --> 01:02:42.893
He's just upstairs, he's going
to flip this whole city

01:02:42.927 --> 01:02:44.394
looking for you.

01:02:44.428 --> 01:02:45.896
I don't know
what you mean.

01:02:45.930 --> 01:02:48.098
We have to finish it.

01:02:48.132 --> 01:02:49.566
Finish what?

01:02:49.599 --> 01:02:51.301
You know what!

01:02:51.335 --> 01:02:53.270
I don't.

01:02:53.303 --> 01:02:55.239
FUCK YOU!

01:02:55.272 --> 01:02:58.275
I must be missing
something right now.

01:02:58.308 --> 01:02:59.409
I'm fucking
sorry alright,

01:02:59.443 --> 01:03:00.744
I didn't know
what I was doing.

01:03:00.777 --> 01:03:03.080
There's nothing
I can do for you.

01:03:03.113 --> 01:03:05.682
I'll get you more money...
I'll get you anything you want.

01:03:09.286 --> 01:03:10.420
I don't know what
you're talking about.

01:03:10.454 --> 01:03:11.688
I'm going to have
to ask you to leave.

01:03:11.721 --> 01:03:12.756
Stop it! Stop!
He's gonna hurt Azaria!

01:03:12.789 --> 01:03:13.991
I'm not going to
let that happen!

01:03:14.024 --> 01:03:16.293
Stop! Stop it!

01:03:16.326 --> 01:03:17.261
Okay...

01:03:17.294 --> 01:03:19.263
I'll get you
anything you want.

01:03:19.296 --> 01:03:21.932
That's just the thing...

01:03:21.966 --> 01:03:24.101
I don't want anything.

01:03:24.134 --> 01:03:25.669
Not from you.

01:03:29.039 --> 01:03:31.441
Let me show you out.

01:03:31.475 --> 01:03:33.477
AHHH!!!

01:03:36.313 --> 01:03:38.815
You stay away from
me you understand!

01:03:38.849 --> 01:03:40.817
Just leave me alone.

01:03:48.658 --> 01:03:54.164
ARG!!!

01:03:54.831 --> 01:03:57.968
(frantic keyboard tapping)

01:03:58.002 --> 01:03:59.169
(keycard beep)

01:04:07.077 --> 01:04:09.179
(frantic breathing)

01:04:09.213 --> 01:04:10.981
What are you doing in here?

01:04:11.015 --> 01:04:12.649
Give me what I need.

01:04:12.682 --> 01:04:15.152
What is that exactly?

01:04:15.185 --> 01:04:16.720
You know what!

01:04:16.753 --> 01:04:19.823
You know I can't-
I can't help you...

01:04:19.856 --> 01:04:23.660
You know I've always wondered
what human flesh tasted like?

01:04:23.693 --> 01:04:26.330
You suppose it would
taste better off the face,

01:04:26.363 --> 01:04:27.831
Please please don't...
or the thigh?

01:04:27.864 --> 01:04:29.833
NO!!!
No! No bitch, no more!

01:04:29.866 --> 01:04:31.368
Get me what I need!

01:04:37.741 --> 01:04:39.609
AH!!!

01:04:45.916 --> 01:04:48.718
No... (sobbing)

01:04:55.425 --> 01:04:56.893
Look at what
you're doing to me!

01:04:56.927 --> 01:04:57.761
Stop it!

01:04:57.794 --> 01:05:02.599
AHH!!!!
Stop it, Stop it!

01:05:02.632 --> 01:05:04.401
God!!!!

01:05:10.240 --> 01:05:15.912
(silence)

01:05:34.098 --> 01:05:36.133
And you don't know where he is.

01:05:36.166 --> 01:05:37.901
No.

01:05:37.934 --> 01:05:40.737
He breaks into lockup,
assaults one of our orderlies,

01:05:40.770 --> 01:05:43.073
and steals medication.

01:05:43.107 --> 01:05:45.242
No Betty. He is not coming back.

01:05:45.275 --> 01:05:46.977
No Betty. He is not coming back.
He didn't assault her.

01:05:47.011 --> 01:05:50.747
